.SH NAME
.PP
\f[B]mkscr\f[R] - make bash script
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IP
.nf
\f[B]
mkscr [--subdirectory|-s \fI<directory>\fP]
      [--template|-t \fI<file>\fP]
      [--generate-help|-g]
      \fI<name>\fP
mkscr --help|-h
\f[R]
.fi
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
Last argument is always the \f[B]\fI<name>\fP\f[R] of the new script
.PP
